* {{audio|en-us-acclimate.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}

===Verb===
{{en-verb|acclimat}}

# {{lb|en|transitive|chiefly|US}} To [[habituate]] to a [[climate]] not native; to [[acclimatize]].
# {{lb|en|transitive|chiefly|US}} To [[adjust]] to a new [[environment]]; not necessarily a wild, natural, earthy one.
# {{lb|en|intransitive|chiefly|US}} To become accustomed to a new climate or environment.

